item.title: Wizzard - I Wish It Could Be Christmas Everyday - Key of D - Ukulaliens - Ukulele Club
item.description: Play along video for the song I Wish It Could Be Christmas Everyday by Wizzard from the channel Ukulaliens - Ukulele Club. Chords used in the song: A, A7, Am, B♭, Cm, D, Dm, Em, F, G, G7.
